props.name: boundaryCount
props.description: Number of always visible pages at the beginning and end

props.name: defaultPage
props.description: The page selected by default when the component is uncontrolled

props.name: disabled
props.description: If true, the component is disabled

props.name: getItemAriaLabel
props.description: Accepts a function which returns a string value that provides a user-friendly name for the current page

props.name: hideNextButton
props.description: If true, hide the next-page button

props.name: hidePrevButton
props.description: If true, hide the previous-page button

props.name: onChange
props.description: Callback fired when the page is changed

props.name: shape
props.description: The shape of the pagination items

props.name: showFirstButton
props.description: If true, show the first-page button

props.name: showLastButton
props.description: If true, show the last-page button

props.name: siblingCount
props.description: Number of always visible pages before and after the current page
